data.description: **$5,000 DISNEY/UNIVERSAL TRIP WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER** Welcome to Cane Bay Plantation, the fourth largest master-planned community in the country! This neighborhood is designed to be a true golf cart community, where you can easily ride to nearby shopping, restaurants, and small businesses, or simply enjoy a leisurely cruise with friends.Situated on a premium pond lot, this brand new home built in 2022 offers a sense of tranquility and privacy. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a spacious two-car garage, a driveway, a full gutter system, and beautifully landscaped surroundings. The pond is stocked with fish, adding to the serene ambiance.Upon entering the front door, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light and scratch-resistant waterproof floors. The tall ceilings and custom details, such as trimmed out doors and five-panel doors, add to the luxurious feel of the home. To the right, you'll find a separate dining room that can also be used as a flex space, such as an office or den.  Continuing through the home, you'll enter the expansive living room with its impressive 20+ foot ceilings and gas fireplace. This open concept space seamlessly connects the breakfast area, kitchen, living room, and small den. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, stainless appliances, craftsman-style white cabinets, a gas stove, custom backsplash, and beautiful pendants and fixtures.  Heading upstairs on the oak tread stairs, you'll find a versatile loft area that can be used as a flex space. This area leads to the bedrooms and bathrooms, including the spacious guest bedrooms with a shared bathroom featuring double vanities and matching countertops and floors.  The master bedroom offers a stunning view of the pond and features tray ceilings. The ensuite bathroom includes double vanity sinks with countertops, white cabinets, a fully tiled showe, scratch-resistant floors, and a large walk-in closet with ample storage space. Additionally, there is a walk-in laundry room with custom shelving for added convenience.  Stepping outside to the back of the property, you'll find a covered patio and a large fully fenced backyard. The 6-foot fences on both sides provide privacy, while the fence at the back leads to the pond, offering beautiful sunset views that the low country is known for.  Woodwinds of Cane Bay is a unique community that offers an array of amenities. The largest YMCA on the East Coast is located here, featuring Olympic-sized swimming pools, basketball courts, softball fields, soccer fields, pickleball courts, tennis courts, a library, and a weight room. The community also hosts food truck nights once a week, providing a fun dining experience. For outdoor enthusiasts, there are plenty of walking and jogging trails to explore.  The brand new amenity center at Woodwinds features an incredible pool and playground area, perfect for both children and adults to enjoy. This community offers a lifestyle unlike any other, and you should definitely consider making it your home!
